data.description: Price reduction!  Motivated Sellers. Bring us an offer! This is the new place you will call HOME!!!! Time to relax in the beautiful backyard and enjoy the refreshing pool! Adored by its Owners for years, this home has been meticulously cared for and loved. This two-bedroom, one-bath pool home boasting a beautiful kitchen open to the dining area, a gorgeous, remodeled bathroom and a bright and comfy living area and Florida Room is "move-in" ready!  This home has newer,   double pain windows and plantation shutters to adjust the perfect light.  The pool has a relaxing waterfall and fiber optic lighting for those quiet evenings.  The roof is less than 3 years old.  Side yard has a gate to park RV, boat, etc. behind fence. Centrally located near shopping, restaurants, & schools, minutes in either direction to downtown St. Pete or the gorgeous Gulf Beaches, quick access to US-19, I-275, and both Tampa and St. Pete/Clearwater Airports.
